OL,5, Israel's envoy to India has apologised 
OL,6, for comments made by Israeli filmmaker 
OL,7, Nadav Lapid on a controversial         
OL,8, Bollywood film on Kashmir.             
OL,10,FNadav Lapid, jury chief at the         
OL,11,FInternational Film Festival India      
OL,12,F(IFFI), criticised the inclusion of The
OL,13,FKashmir Files at the event.            
OL,15,FDescribing the film as "propaganda", he
OL,16,Fsaid he was "shocked" that it was      
OL,17,Fincluded in competition category.      
OL,19,FA huge commercial hit, the film had    
OL,20,Fsparked controversy during its release.
